What? You don't want a beer? What's wrong?

00:00:54.021 --> 00:00:55.021
I...

00:00:55.313 --> 00:00:58.021
got the results back
from the detective exam.

00:00:58.105 --> 00:01:01.105
You failed again?
This is why I never took that test.

00:01:01.188 --> 00:01:03.313
All the anxiety and disappointment.

00:01:03.396 --> 00:01:06.105
At some point, you have to realize
you have hit your ceiling

00:01:06.188 --> 00:01:07.355
and just give up.

00:01:07.438 --> 00:01:09.478
You know, you should go around
and speak at schools.

00:01:09.521 --> 00:01:12.313
- That was very inspiring.
- I should. Kids need to hear this shit.

00:01:12.396 --> 00:01:13.396
I don't get it, man.

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:16.313
I know all the answers,
I just freeze under pressure.

00:01:16.396 --> 00:01:18.855
You know, I can't take the exam
for, like, three more months,

00:01:18.938 --> 00:01:20.563
so I gotta continue lying to Audrey.

00:01:20.646 --> 00:01:22.355
So when we're at dinner tonight, please,

00:01:22.438 --> 00:01:23.813
- tell your wi...
- Ah! No.

00:01:23.896 --> 00:01:26.271
Come on, man.
You know I'll lie for you anytime.

00:01:26.355 --> 00:01:28.396
I will cover up dead bodies for you.

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:32.605
But if I ask Holly to lie to your wife,
there's no way we're messing around.

00:01:32.688 --> 00:01:33.771
It's Freaky Friday!

00:01:33.855 --> 00:01:36.813
You don't have to lie,
just tell her to ignore when I'm lying.

00:01:36.896 --> 00:01:37.896
That's it.

00:01:38.730 --> 00:01:39.980
- Okay, fine.
- Thank you.

00:01:40.063 --> 00:01:41.438
You owe me.

00:01:41.521 --> 00:01:42.521
See you tonight.

00:01:45.646 --> 00:01:47.771
I gotta get Claritin. Claritin.

00:01:47.855 --> 00:01:49.563
Oh, my God! Look!

00:01:50.271 --> 00:01:51.855
He took her in a helicopter?

00:01:52.146 --> 00:01:54.230
My husband won't even pay for Uber Black.

00:01:54.313 --> 00:01:57.855
Yeah. I don't even...
I can't even remember the last time

00:01:57.938 --> 00:02:01.563
that Nick did anything
even remotely romantic.

00:02:01.813 --> 00:02:04.855
I mean, he used to leave me,
like, cute little mixtapes,

00:02:05.105 --> 00:02:07.021
little love notes in the bathroom.

00:02:07.105 --> 00:02:08.313
Love notes are dead.

00:02:08.396 --> 00:02:09.756
When my husband wants to have sex,

00:02:09.813 --> 00:02:11.733
he just texts me the eggplant
and doughnut emoji.

00:02:12.021 --> 00:02:13.521
Eggplant and doughnut...

00:02:14.438 --> 00:02:15.938
Oh. He's the eggplant.

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:18.188
More like a fingerling potato.

00:02:18.271 --> 00:02:19.664
It doesn't take that much.

00:02:19.688 --> 00:02:22.063
There are guys at the intersection
selling flowers.

00:02:22.146 --> 00:02:24.605
You just roll down the window,
grab a bunch, bring 'em home.

00:02:24.688 --> 00:02:27.521
- I mean, they couldn't make it any easier.
- No kidding.

00:02:27.605 --> 00:02:29.980
I mean, tomorrow
is our 15th wedding anniversary.

00:02:30.521 --> 00:02:33.688
I'm still waiting on that trip to Europe
he promised me on our wedding day.

00:02:33.771 --> 00:02:35.605
- That's been 15 years?
- Yeah.

00:02:35.688 --> 00:02:37.648
I could have walked to Europe by now.

00:02:37.730 --> 00:02:39.271
You know, you just have to tell him.

00:02:39.355 --> 00:02:43.146
I just don't want to have to tell him.
I just want him to know.

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:44.938
- No, they never just know.
- I know.

00:02:45.021 --> 00:02:47.164
- That doesn't happen.
- You have to tell men everything.

00:02:47.188 --> 00:02:49.581
If you want the dishes to not go
in the sink, you have to tell them.

00:02:49.605 --> 00:02:51.525
If you want him to shower
before he comes to bed,

00:02:51.605 --> 00:02:52.855
- you have to ask him.
- Ugh.

00:02:52.938 --> 00:02:55.313
That's why they have those signs
in bathrooms at restaurants

00:02:55.396 --> 00:02:57.396
to tell employees to wash their hands.

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:59.646
Those aren't for women, guys.
Those are for men.

00:02:59.730 --> 00:03:02.730
Or maybe you could just text him,
airplane, wine glass,

00:03:02.813 --> 00:03:05.730
Italian flag, eggplant,
doughnut, doughnut, doughnut.

00:03:25.271 --> 00:03:26.355
Let's go with the 50.

00:03:31.563 --> 00:03:32.646
Claritin...

00:03:40.563 --> 00:03:41.563
Hi, welcome.

00:03:42.146 --> 00:03:43.146
Thank you.

00:03:43.188 --> 00:03:44.831
Thanks a lot.

00:03:44.855 --> 00:03:47.396
Are you gonna tell 'em
about the stuff in your backpack?

00:03:47.730 --> 00:03:49.650
Mind your own business, man.
I'm paying for this.

00:03:50.188 --> 00:03:52.063
I like your sneakers.
They must be expensive.

00:03:52.146 --> 00:03:54.313
Is that why can't afford
the Monster Energy Drink

00:03:54.396 --> 00:03:55.896
