That's...

00:06:01.855 --> 00:06:04.271
Guarantee me of wanting to
wake up and leave.

00:06:08.938 --> 00:06:11.146
What's the matter?
You didn't like that joke?

00:06:13.521 --> 00:06:14.688
I'm flossing.

