And I plan on getting blind drunk
and ruining the festivities.

00:13:01.521 --> 00:13:03.396
Okay. I support that.

00:13:03.730 --> 00:13:05.563
- I say, Audrey...
- Hm.

00:13:06.605 --> 00:13:09.230
Do you and your husband
have plans this weekend?

